CourseRepository --> AppDbContext

%% === INTERFACE REALIZATION ===
CourseModerationService ..|> ICourseModerationService
CourseRepository ..|> ICourseRepository

%% === DEPENDENCY ===
AdminModerationControllerFE ..> AdminModerationControllerBE
AdminModerationControllerFE ..> CourseModerationViewModel
AdminModerationControllerBE ..> ModerationFilterDto
AdminModerationControllerBE ..> CourseModerationDto
CourseModerationService ..> ModerationFilterDto
CourseModerationService ..> CourseModerationDto
CourseRepository ..> ModerationFilterDto
CourseRepository ..> CourseModerationDto
CourseRepository ..> Course
CourseRepository ..> Instructor

